1
00:00:02,984 --> 00:00:07,241
<i>A survival show crowning K-POP's top boy group.</i>

2
00:00:07,241 --> 00:00:08,942
<i>National producers,</i>

3
00:00:08,942 --> 00:00:13,213
<i>pick the best members yourselves.</i>

4
00:00:19,666 --> 00:00:22,289
[Yoon Soo An]
You made it to the final stage.

5
00:00:22,289 --> 00:00:23,490
How does it feel?

6
00:00:23,490 --> 00:00:24,925
It hasn't sunk in.

7
00:00:24,925 --> 00:00:27,194
Thank you for the kind words.

8
00:00:27,194 --> 00:00:29,321
I'll work harder.

9
00:00:30,490 --> 00:00:32,000
Through the rough times,

10
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:35,101
was there anyone you leaned on?

11
00:00:52,719 --> 00:00:54,334
Hyun Jae and Soo An,

12
00:00:54,334 --> 00:00:56,831
people say you two must be dating.

13
00:00:56,831 --> 00:00:58,625
That rumor's out there.

14
00:00:58,625 --> 00:01:00,089
Is it true?

15
00:01:00,089 --> 00:01:01,734
Come on...

16
00:01:01,734 --> 00:01:03,263
Yeah, it's true.

17
00:01:03,263 --> 00:01:04,669
Huh?

18
00:01:04,669 --> 00:01:07,129
What, am I wrong?

19
00:01:07,129 --> 00:01:09,349
Hey, knock it off.

20
00:01:09,349 --> 00:01:10,669
What's wrong?

21
00:01:10,669 --> 00:01:13,089
Not just for the cameras, right?

22
00:01:13,089 --> 00:01:15,141
Does it look that way?

23
00:01:17,611 --> 00:01:19,872
[AI Alert: Mallangs Swoon Moments]

24
00:01:19,872 --> 00:01:22,987
<i>No way, it looked so real.</i>

25
00:01:23,709 --> 00:01:24,702
Seriously?

26
00:01:24,702 --> 00:01:26,386
<i>Props to AI.</i>

27
00:01:26,386 --> 00:01:28,155
<i>These two keep me going.</i>

28
00:01:28,155 --> 00:01:31,191
<i>I really want them to debut together.</i>

29
00:01:31,191 --> 00:01:32,910
[Soo An out by one rank? No way]

30
00:01:32,910 --> 00:01:34,500
[Splitting them up? Brutal]

31
00:01:38,198 --> 00:01:40,701
[Mirae Times: Final 6 'Wakers' Debut]

32
00:01:40,701 --> 00:01:43,610
- Waker! Hi, we're Wakers.
- Waker! Hi, we're Wakers.

33
00:01:43,610 --> 00:01:46,745
[One-year contract run ahead]

34
00:01:48,300 --> 00:01:52,445
<i>♪ Happy birthday ♪</i>

35
00:01:58,251 --> 00:01:59,798
['Wakers' Ending, No Renewal]

36
00:01:59,798 --> 00:02:01,343
[Wakers Goodbye Fan Meeting In September]

37
00:02:01,343 --> 00:02:04,000
<i>Wait, a year already?</i>

38
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:06,300
<i>What about the trainees who got cut?</i>

39
00:02:06,300 --> 00:02:07,361
<i>Right?</i>

40
00:02:07,361 --> 00:02:09,334
<i>Anyone still remember Mallangs?</i>

41
00:02:09,334 --> 00:02:12,432
<i>What's Soo An up to?</i>

42
00:02:19,367 --> 00:02:22,709
<i>Alright, eyes on Hyun Jae.</i>

43
00:02:27,948 --> 00:02:29,375
[Hyun Jae]

44
00:02:29,375 --> 00:02:31,988
<i>Looks good.</i>

45
00:02:31,988 --> 00:02:34,921
<i>That's a wrap for the stand-ins.</i>

46
00:02:35,792 --> 00:02:37,601
[Wakers Goodbye Fan Meeting]

47
00:02:37,601 --> 00:02:40,035
<i>When the members arrive in an hour,</i>

48
00:02:40,035 --> 00:02:42,788
<i>we'll jump right into rehearsal.</i>

49
00:02:42,788 --> 00:02:44,998
<i>Mark your spots now,</i>

50
00:02:44,998 --> 00:02:47,768
<i>and recheck the rest of the setup.</i>

51
00:02:47,768 --> 00:02:49,936
[Se Beom]

52
00:02:54,501 --> 00:02:57,210
<i>Okay, come on down.</i>

53
00:03:00,100 --> 00:03:02,915
Hurry down and clear the gear.

54
00:03:13,694 --> 00:03:16,930
Honestly, Soo An,

55
00:03:16,930 --> 00:03:19,666
the stage suits you.

56
00:03:19,666 --> 00:03:21,100
Why didn't you tell me?

57
00:03:21,100 --> 00:03:22,495
Huh?

58
00:03:25,267 --> 00:03:28,501
Oh, I didn't mention it?

59
00:03:28,501 --> 00:03:29,776
Thought I had.

60
00:03:29,776 --> 00:03:32,504
My head's everywhere lately.

61
00:03:32,504 --> 00:03:34,915
You're stuck at home too much. I worry.

62
00:03:34,915 --> 00:03:38,138
Get out, meet people, breathe a little.

63
00:03:40,992 --> 00:03:43,390
I know Hyun Jae makes you uneasy,

64
00:03:43,390 --> 00:03:45,492
but Yoon Soo An, you've worked sets. You know.

65
00:03:45,492 --> 00:03:46,827
Can you recall a single crew face?

66
00:03:46,827 --> 00:03:48,195
Has anyone ever spoken to you?

67
00:03:48,195 --> 00:03:50,964
You won't run into Hyun Jae.

68
00:03:50,964 --> 00:03:52,334
Don't worry.

69
00:03:52,334 --> 00:03:54,668
Wakers just pulled up. Move fast, please.

70
00:03:54,668 --> 00:03:57,837
Don't hang around. Go haul boxes from the lot.

71
00:04:10,884 --> 00:04:13,653
We're late, Hyun Jae. Get out.

72
00:04:33,767 --> 00:04:35,654
Do you need help?

73
00:04:38,634 --> 00:04:40,639
I'm good.

74
00:04:47,968 --> 00:04:51,667
<i>Public opinion shaped by mass media
shapes everything.</i>

75
00:04:51,667 --> 00:04:55,254
- Who's Shin Jae Min?
<i>- That's why the press</i>

76
00:04:55,254 --> 00:04:57,431
- He's never come to class, right?
<i>- is a double-edged sword.</i>

77
00:04:57,431 --> 00:04:58,565
Does anyone know him?

78
00:04:58,565 --> 00:05:00,534
He's in the group chat.

79
00:05:00,534 --> 00:05:02,601
<i>A year ago,</i>

80
00:05:02,601 --> 00:05:05,806
<i>on the audition show Next Stage,</i>

81
00:05:05,806 --> 00:05:07,567
<i>we found</i>

82
00:05:07,567 --> 00:05:09,182
<i>- one such case.</i>
- Team 4?

83
00:05:10,801 --> 00:05:13,647
<i>Some contestants rode scandals into favor</i>

84
00:05:13,647 --> 00:05:16,149
<i>and gained popularity,</i>

85
00:05:16,149 --> 00:05:18,285
<i>but it went the other way too.</i>

86
00:05:18,285 --> 00:05:19,701
[Next Stage Contestant Lee Jae Min
Stalking Scandal]

87
00:05:19,701 --> 00:05:20,654
- No way.
- What?

88
00:05:20,654 --> 00:05:22,234
<i>This contestant Lee Jae Min</i>

89
00:05:22,234 --> 00:05:25,025
<i>was a front-runner for the debut lineup,</i>

90
00:05:25,025 --> 00:05:26,861
<i>riding high on popularity,</i>

91
00:05:26,861 --> 00:05:31,764
<i>when news broke
that he stalked a famous idol...</i>

92
00:05:35,100 --> 00:05:37,601
Presenter, wrap it up.

93
00:05:37,601 --> 00:05:39,634
<i>Right.</i>

94
00:05:39,634 --> 00:05:41,109
<i>So, as you see...</i>

95
00:05:41,109 --> 00:05:43,628
<i>Mass media's power is huge.</i>

96
00:05:43,628 --> 00:05:47,214
<i>That's why fact-checking must be airtight,</i>

97
00:05:47,214 --> 00:05:51,817
<i>so innocent people don't get hurt.</i>

98
00:05:52,519 --> 00:05:54,921
Any questions?

99
00:06:02,434 --> 00:06:05,708
In the case, it's Shin Jae Min, not Lee.

100
00:06:05,708 --> 00:06:07,368
[Contestant Lee Jae Min Stalking Scandal]
Fact-checking matters.

101
00:06:07,368 --> 00:06:08,601
What, who is he?

102
00:06:08,601 --> 00:06:10,501
- Who?
- Isn't he the stalker?

103
00:06:10,501 --> 00:06:11,801
- Stalker?
- Really? Shin Jae Min?

104
00:06:11,801 --> 00:06:13,868
Where?

105
00:06:13,868 --> 00:06:15,067
I think it's really him.

106
00:06:15,067 --> 00:06:17,801
Shin Jae Min goes here?

107
00:06:17,801 --> 00:06:20,100
<i>- I'm sorry.</i>
- Why is he here?

108
00:06:20,100 --> 00:06:23,055
This is insane.

109
00:06:24,885 --> 00:06:27,513
Any more questions?

110
00:06:27,513 --> 00:06:31,413
If not, let's wrap up today.

111
00:06:32,492 --> 00:06:34,186
Nice work.

112
00:06:37,943 --> 00:06:40,783
<i>I already asked to switch groups.</i>

113
00:06:40,783 --> 00:06:42,703
<i>It's too uncomfortable.</i>

114
00:06:42,703 --> 00:06:44,303
<i>Stalking is a crime.</i>

115
00:06:44,303 --> 00:06:46,903
<i>I won't team up with a criminal.</i>

116
00:06:46,903 --> 00:06:49,823
<i>This is the group chat.</i>

117
00:06:49,823 --> 00:06:52,279
<i>I'll drop the class.</i>

118
00:06:52,279 --> 00:06:54,413
<i>You don't need to switch.</i>

119
00:07:22,192 --> 00:07:25,196
Wakers, camera rehearsal starts.

120
00:07:26,046 --> 00:07:28,114
The green room's empty, toss the trash

121
00:07:28,114 --> 00:07:30,917
and restock the snacks.

122
00:07:30,917 --> 00:07:33,367
I'll do it.

123
00:07:52,439 --> 00:07:54,207
<i>I'll debut too,</i>

124
00:07:54,207 --> 00:07:55,742
<i>so let's meet again.</i>

125
00:07:55,742 --> 00:07:58,911
<i>Yeah, we will.</i>

126
00:07:59,834 --> 00:08:02,081
<i>Let's stop here.</i>

127
00:08:02,949 --> 00:08:04,918
<i>We'll skip the next song</i>

128
00:08:04,918 --> 00:08:07,634
<i>and move to segment three.</i>

129
00:08:07,634 --> 00:08:09,322
<i>It's the fan meeting game,</i>

130
00:08:09,322 --> 00:08:12,224
<i>so check the members' props,</i>

131
00:08:13,438 --> 00:08:16,597
<i>and we'll roll once you're set.</i>

132
00:08:16,597 --> 00:08:20,032
<i>Crew, move quickly, please.</i>

133
00:08:26,667 --> 00:08:28,441
Hyun Jae, hurry back.

134
00:08:28,441 --> 00:08:31,043
Okay, one sec.

135
00:08:32,479 --> 00:08:33,686
[Cast Green Room: Wakers]

136
00:08:43,767 --> 00:08:46,192
Where's that scarf?

137
00:09:23,534 --> 00:09:25,983
Hyun Jae, we're starting.

138
00:09:25,983 --> 00:09:27,767
Coming!

139
00:10:33,400 --> 00:10:36,303
That's chili paste.

140
00:10:36,303 --> 00:10:37,440
What?

141
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:40,534
Oh, you're foreign.

142
00:10:40,534 --> 00:10:42,267
That's not ketchup.

143
00:10:42,267 --> 00:10:44,223
This is ketchup.

144
00:10:47,609 --> 00:10:49,648
Thanks.

145
00:10:51,934 --> 00:10:53,886
Shake it.

146
00:12:02,067 --> 00:12:03,400
Your number,

147
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:04,636
please.

148
00:12:04,636 --> 00:12:05,901
That was bold.

149
00:12:05,901 --> 00:12:07,476
<i>You won't pick up.</i>

150
00:12:07,476 --> 00:12:08,634
<i>Hey, where are you?</i>

151
00:12:08,634 --> 00:12:10,300
I'm home.

152
00:12:10,300 --> 00:12:11,631
I saw him.

153
00:12:11,631 --> 00:12:12,676
<i>What?</i>

154
00:12:12,676 --> 00:12:15,334
Well, look who it is.

155
00:12:15,334 --> 00:12:18,216
Don't slack off just because the group's done.

156
00:12:18,216 --> 00:12:19,907
Plenty of eyes are on you.

157
00:12:19,907 --> 00:12:22,476
You're a contestant, and he's an active idol...

158
00:12:22,476 --> 00:12:24,534
His agency

159
00:12:24,534 --> 00:12:26,236
released a statement.

160
00:12:26,236 --> 00:12:29,382
Did something really happen?

161
00:12:29,382 --> 00:12:31,496
With that idol.

